  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "Work needs to be done to the cgroups lib and containerd metrics interfaces to support cgroups v2 support.  With much of the work in 5.3 kernels this should be reasonable to start supporting as a first class feature and can be a replacement for v1 for some users.\r\n\r\nrunc recently gained support for v2 as well as crun.\r\n\r\n---\r\n(below are edited by maintainers)\r\n\r\n## runc checklist\r\nSee https://github.com/opencontainers/runc/issues/2315\r\n\r\n## containerd checklist\r\n- [x] base https://github.com/containerd/containerd/pull/3799\r\n- [x] PID metrics https://github.com/containerd/containerd/pull/3799\r\n- [x] CPU metrics\r\n- [x] Memory metrics\r\n- [x] OOM handler: https://github.com/containerd/containerd/pull/4273\r\n- [x] IO metrics: https://github.com/containerd/containerd/pull/3919\r\n\r\n## containerd/CRI checklist\r\n- [x]  metrics: https://github.com/containerd/cri/pull/1376\r\n- [x] [enable cgroup namespace by default](https://github.com/containers/libpod/issues/4363): https://github.com/containerd/cri/pull/1371\r\n- enable cgroup namespace for pod sandboxes as well as for containers? (To be determined)\r\n- [x] disable cgroup namespace for privileged pods (discussed in https://github.com/kubernetes/enhancements/pull/1370): https://github.com/containerd/cri/pull/1415\r\n- systemd cgroup driver for rootless (seems working without additional work: https://github.com/AkihiroSuda/critest-rootless-cgroup2)\r\n\r\n## CI\r\n- [x] CI (crun): https://github.com/containerd/containerd/pull/4279\r\n- [X] CI (runc): https://github.com/containerd/containerd/pull/4408\r\n- CI for rootless mode with systemd (will be a follow-up PR)",
